{"title":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","slug":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","date":"2019-11-13T01:54:56.000Z","updated":"2019-11-18T08:21:49.213Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/build-linux-kenel-in-qumu.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"еңЁQEMUдёӯиҝҗиЎҢзј–иҜ‘зҡ„LinuxеҶ…ж ё","covers":["https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/1zoMHxPZeOBiFSr.jpg","https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg"],"content":"<h2 id=\"еңЁQEMUдёӯиҝҗиЎҢзј–иҜ‘зҡ„LinuxеҶ…ж ё\"><a href=\"#еңЁQEMUдёӯиҝҗиЎҢзј–иҜ‘зҡ„LinuxеҶ…ж ё\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"еңЁQEMUдёӯиҝҗиЎҢзј–иҜ‘зҡ„LinuxеҶ…ж ё\"></a>еңЁ<code>QEMU</code>дёӯиҝҗиЎҢзј–иҜ‘зҡ„<code>Linux</code>еҶ…ж ё</h2><a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"еҶ…ж ёзј–иҜ‘и„ҡжң¬-build-sh\"><a href=\"#еҶ…ж ёзј–иҜ‘и„ҡжң¬-build-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"еҶ…ж ёзј–иҜ‘и„ҡжң¬ build.sh\"></a>еҶ…ж ёзј–иҜ‘и„ҡжң¬ <code>build.sh</code></h3><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export ARCH=arm</span><br><span class=\"line\">export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extra</span><br><span class=\"line\">export CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi-</span><br><span class=\"line\">make LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</span><br><span class=\"line\">make zImage -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make modules -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make dtbs</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/zImage extra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/dts/*ca9.dtb\textra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp .config extra/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li><p>й»ҳи®Өзҡ„еҶ…ж ёй…ҚзҪ®ж–Үд»¶дёә <code>LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</code>.дёҠиҝ°и„ҡжң¬дјҡе°ҶиҮӘеҠЁзј–иҜ‘еҘҪзҡ„<code>zImage,dtbs</code>еӨҚеҲ¶еҲ°<code>extra</code>зӣ®еҪ•дёӯ</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>extra</code>зӣ®еҪ•дёӢзҡ„vexpressжҳҜдёҖеј иҷҡжӢҹзҡ„SDеҚЎпјҢдҪңдёә<em>ж №ж–Үд»¶зі»з»ҹ</em>зҡ„еӯҳж”ҫд»ӢиҙЁгҖӮе®ғиғҪд»Ҙ<code>loop</code>еҪўејҸиў«жҢӮиҪҪ<code>mount</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"зј–иҜ‘жЁЎеқ—зҡ„и„ҡжң¬-module-sh\"><a href=\"#зј–иҜ‘жЁЎеқ—зҡ„и„ҡжң¬-module-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"зј–иҜ‘жЁЎеқ—зҡ„и„ҡжң¬ module.sh\"></a>зј–иҜ‘жЁЎеқ—зҡ„и„ҡжң¬ <code>module.sh</code></h3><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules_install INSTALL_MOD_PATH=extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo umount extra/img</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li>е®ғдјҡиҮӘеҠЁзј–иҜ‘еҶ…ж ёжЁЎеқ—е№¶е®үиЈ…еҲ°<code>vexprees.img</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"еҗҜеҠЁеёҰLCDзҡ„ARM-LinuxеҶ…-ж ё\"><a href=\"#еҗҜеҠЁеёҰLCDзҡ„ARM-LinuxеҶ…-ж ё\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"еҗҜеҠЁеёҰLCDзҡ„ARM LinuxеҶ… ж ё\"></a>еҗҜеҠЁеёҰ<code>LCD</code>зҡ„<code>ARM Linux</code>еҶ… ж ё</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg\" alt=\"01-arm-linux-qemu-lcd.jpg\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"зј–иҜ‘з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„linuxеҶ…ж ёжЁЎеқ—\"><a href=\"#зј–иҜ‘з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„linuxеҶ…ж ёжЁЎеқ—\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"зј–иҜ‘з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„linuxеҶ…ж ёжЁЎеқ—\"></a>зј–иҜ‘з®ҖеҚ•зҡ„<code>linux</code>еҶ…ж ёжЁЎеқ—</h2><!--more-->\n<h3 id=\"hello-c\"><a href=\"#hello-c\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hello.c\"></a><code>hello.c</code></h3><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * a simple kernel module: hello</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Copyright (C) 2014 Barry Song  (baohua@kernel.org)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Licensed under GPLv2 or later.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/init.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/module.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> __<span class=\"function\">init <span class=\"title\">hello_init</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tprintk(KERN_INFO <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World in hjl's linux\\n\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">module_init(hello_init);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> __<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> <span class=\"title\">hello_exit</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tprintk(KERN_INFO <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World exit byebye\\n \"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">module_exit(hello_exit);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_AUTHOR(<span class=\"string\">\"Hu Jinlei &lt;hjl2016060203025@std.uestc.edu.cn&gt;\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_LICENSE(<span class=\"string\">\"GPL v2\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_DESCRIPTION(<span class=\"string\">\"A simple Hello World Module\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_ALIAS(<span class=\"string\">\"a simplest module\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ol>\n<li>зј–иҜ‘</li>\n<li><code>insmod ./hello.ko</code>еҠ иҪҪ</li>\n<li><code>rmmod hello</code>еҚёиҪҪ</li>\n<li><code>lsmod</code>жҳҫзӨәеҠ иҪҪзҡ„жЁЎеқ—</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/1zoMHxPZeOBiFSr.jpg\" alt=\"03-arm-linux-module.jpg\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"linux-еҶ…ж ёзҡ„й…ҚзҪ®\"><a href=\"#linux-еҶ…ж ёзҡ„й…ҚзҪ®\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux еҶ…ж ёзҡ„й…ҚзҪ®\"></a><code>linux</code> еҶ…ж ёзҡ„й…ҚзҪ®</h2><!--more-->\n<h3 id=\"еӣӣз§Қжү“ејҖж–№ејҸ\"><a href=\"#еӣӣз§Қжү“ејҖж–№ејҸ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"еӣӣз§Қжү“ејҖж–№ејҸ\"></a>еӣӣз§Қжү“ејҖж–№ејҸ</h3><ul>\n<li><p><code>make config</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make menuconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make xconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make gconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>menuconfig</code> еҰӮдёӢжүҖзӨә</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg\" alt=\"01-arm-linux-qemu-lcd.jpg\"></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":3,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":2,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"}]}